Package: chrombinarize
Title: A series of functions used in ChromBinarize's pipelines
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "Sam", 
        family = "Fletcher", 
        email = "s.o.fletcher@exeter.ac.uk", 
        role = c("aut","cre")
        )
Description: Functions used to binarize methylation (and hydroxymethylation) 
    data into a binary file format that is useable by ChromHMM. It also
    provides some supplementary functionality to give the user more information
    around the statistical thresholds being used in the binarization process.
